on has announced his retirement from swimming only a few months before the Paris Games that were expected to be his swansong.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mack_Horton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mack Horton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mack_Horton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mack_Horton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"MACK HORTON/INSTAGRAM PublishedJan\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"MELBOURNE-Former Olympic champion\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"his swansong\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old Australian, who won the 400 metres freestyle gold at the 2016 Rio Olympics, said he no longer felt he was able to give his best to the sport.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 651, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.99958075935055, \"rank\": 0.0004151793756791326, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400 metres freestyle gold\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Rio Olympics\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I dearly wanted to swim in Paris but the hunger wasn't there,\\\" Horton, who recently got married, said in a Swimming Australia media statement.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999819133337, \"rank\": 1.80865901785229e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 858, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\", \"score\": 0.9990672487318941, \"rank\": 0.0009311991001641317, \"text\": \"Horton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Swimming Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Swimming Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hunger\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always want to give my all and I am not someone who just wants to make up the numbers, so this is the right time to step away.\\\"\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later told the Sydney Morning Herald: \\\"Usually when I am not satisfied with a swim, I will touch the wall and there is clarity - 'This is what I need to fix, this is what I need to do' - and I am really motivated to do it.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Sydney Morning Herald\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"a swim\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I touched the wall and for the first time ever, I had none of that.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had done everything that anyone has ever asked of me.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had tried as hard as I can and I just did not know if I could go faster.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Up until that moment, I believed my best would still beat the best in the world...\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no point doing it if I do not believe my best is going to win.\\\"\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no point\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to his Olympic gold, he won a bronze in the 4x200m free at the postponed Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"the postponed Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won a gold in the same event at the 2019 Gwangju world championships.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_p